    "Using nine frequency bins, the median and central 90% credible regions for log 10 ṅ0 /[Mpc 3 Gyr] are -1.95 +2.91 -5.87 and -3.51 +0.59 -0.62 for the agnostic and astrophysically-informed models, respectively.",
